                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path>
                </svg>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                Show <strong>line items</strong> — equipment, labor, materials — because itemized quotes build trust and win against single-number bids. Keep internal numbers like your overhead percentage and margin private; customers should see what they get, not your cost accounting.
              </p>
            </details>

